{"text_id":41675,"tokens":["In"," this"," paper",","," we"," investigate"," the"," two","-","qu","bit"," entanglement"," in"," an"," $","XYZ","$"," magnetic"," chain"," with"," D","zy","al","osh","inski","i","-","M","oriya"," (","DM",")"," antis","ymmetric"," anisotropic"," exchange"," interaction","."," We"," employ"," the"," Heisenberg"," model"," to"," describe"," the"," system"," and"," use"," the"," concurrence"," as"," a"," measure"," of"," entanglement","."," Our"," results"," reveal"," that"," the"," DM"," interaction"," significantly"," influences"," the"," entanglement"," properties"," of"," the"," system",","," particularly"," in"," the"," presence"," of"," an"," external"," magnetic"," field","."," We"," also"," explore"," the"," effects"," of"," anisotropy"," and"," find"," that"," it"," can"," enhance"," or"," suppress"," the"," entanglement"," depending"," on"," the"," direction"," of"," the"," magnetic"," field","."," Furthermore",","," we"," demonstrate"," that"," the"," entanglement"," can"," be"," manipulated"," by"," adjusting"," the"," DM"," interaction"," and"," the"," magnetic"," field","."," Our"," findings"," provide"," valuable"," insights"," into"," the"," control"," of"," quantum"," entanglement"," in"," spin"," chains",","," which"," is"," crucial"," for"," the"," development"," of"," quantum"," information"," processing"," and"," quantum"," computing","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt4","label":1}